bibliothek.gui.dock.station

Class StationDropItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • bibliothek.gui.dock.station.StationDropItem

  • public class StationDropItem
extends Object
    This class offers information about a Dockable that is going to be dropped. The properties include:
    • The dockable itself
    • The location of the mouse on the screen mouseX and mouseY
    • the location of the title on the screen titleX and titleY
    Author:
    Benjamin Sigg
